Products.SmallFormatDescription: Moving Mountains Plant Based Vegan Burger
Products.FullDescription: Moving Mountains Plant Based Vegan Burger
Products.RichDescription:
Bite into the future with vegan 100% plant based burger - No Beef, All Leaf!
This vegan burger will delight vegans and fool even the most committed carnivore!
Unlike other alternatives made solely from soy, pea or wheat proteins, the vegan Moving Mountain burger utilises the health properties of mushrooms and the base ingredient.
Each burger contains zero cholesterol and packed with plant protein.
Moving Mountain use plant-based and natural ingredients to recreate the succulence and appearance of meat and is not lab grown.
It bleeds, cooks and browns like a real beef burger by using natural beetroot juices.
